WEBVTT

01:38.200 --> 01:40.570
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.200 --> 01:43.690
[Episode 7]

02:33.190 --> 02:33.990
Sweet, right?

02:37.190 --> 02:38.310
Sour as hell.

02:44.680 --> 02:45.750
It's sweet.

02:48.000 --> 02:49.590
It's because there's bitterness
in your heart.

02:49.590 --> 02:51.320
Everything tastes sour to you.

02:54.120 --> 02:55.000
Tell me.

02:55.470 --> 02:57.070
How did you and Lu meet?

03:00.280 --> 03:01.080
Wanna hear?

03:03.560 --> 03:04.360
Twenty taels.

03:08.630 --> 03:09.590
Here's 50.

03:09.710 --> 03:10.640
Keep the change.

03:11.360 --> 03:13.150
I meant gold.

03:20.750 --> 03:21.520
Fine.

03:22.910 --> 03:24.560
It's a slow day anyway,

03:25.000 --> 03:26.630
and I have nothing pressing.

03:27.570 --> 03:28.850
I'll tell you about it.

03:32.820 --> 03:33.790
He and I...

03:35.520 --> 03:37.240
met 11 years ago.

03:39.030 --> 03:41.560
That was the first time
we ever saw each other.

03:42.000 --> 03:44.060
Thank you for sending me home, Mr. Fu.

03:44.840 --> 03:46.170
You're too polite, sir.

03:46.280 --> 03:47.840
It's an honor for the Li household

03:47.840 --> 03:48.870
to have you personally instruct

03:48.870 --> 03:50.530
our young master in painting.

03:52.000 --> 03:53.120
That day,

03:53.630 --> 03:54.470
I wore my

03:54.470 --> 03:55.590
prettiest dress.

03:56.960 --> 03:58.290
Unfortunately, I fell.

03:58.960 --> 04:01.360
My dress got dirty,
and my face got smudged.

04:01.910 --> 04:03.240
I must've looked awful.

04:08.840 --> 04:09.570
Are you okay?

04:11.520 --> 04:12.360
But...

04:13.430 --> 04:14.630
he didn't mind,

04:15.710 --> 04:17.310
and he even escorted me home.

04:18.920 --> 04:20.120
Only later did I learn

04:21.269 --> 04:23.070
he was my new neighbor.

04:26.070 --> 04:27.310
He was a painter

04:28.190 --> 04:29.520
with excellent skills.

04:30.630 --> 04:31.830
People said

04:32.110 --> 04:33.600
he was a man of great learning—

04:33.600 --> 04:34.870
no ordinary person.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.310
He hardly ate—

04:42.870 --> 04:45.330
sometimes not even a single meal
in two days.

04:45.680 --> 04:48.480
He was so thin
you could see his bones sticking out.

04:48.750 --> 04:49.600
Seeing that,

04:50.390 --> 04:52.360
I would often bring him food.

04:53.560 --> 04:54.830
But as time passed,

04:55.560 --> 04:56.310
my feelings

04:57.310 --> 04:59.360
for him slowly faded,

05:00.040 --> 05:01.500
and I saw him less and less.

05:03.720 --> 05:05.580
That was the sensible thing to do.

05:08.270 --> 05:09.470
But half a year later,

05:11.190 --> 05:13.800
a catastrophe

05:14.680 --> 05:16.280
fell upon our escort agency.

05:17.720 --> 05:20.270
An escort agency deals in
trade and transport.

05:20.270 --> 05:21.720
so paying taxes to the government

05:21.720 --> 05:22.650
is only natural.

05:23.680 --> 05:24.480
But that year,

05:25.270 --> 05:27.710
the taxes had become outrageously high.

05:29.160 --> 05:30.070
My father said

05:30.800 --> 05:32.330
it was the Immortality Tax.

05:32.920 --> 05:34.920
Those in power sought eternal life,

05:36.000 --> 05:38.330
and naturally, that required resources.

05:39.000 --> 05:40.120
But they seized

05:40.440 --> 05:41.720
those resources from the hands

05:41.720 --> 05:43.120
of common people like us.

05:43.360 --> 05:44.190
At first,

05:44.870 --> 05:45.950
the Immortality Tax

05:45.950 --> 05:47.810
was only collected in Dongxiang.

05:48.920 --> 05:50.920
But the cost must've been too great.

05:51.040 --> 05:53.170
The tax was extended to other regions.

05:54.800 --> 05:56.000
And our escort agency

05:57.040 --> 05:58.440
was drawn into its reach.

06:00.040 --> 06:01.330
For a living, my father

06:01.800 --> 06:04.800
planned to move the whole family back
to our hometown.

06:05.190 --> 06:06.020
But they...

06:07.820 --> 06:09.430
wouldn't let us go.

06:14.950 --> 06:15.740
Father!

06:40.500 --> 06:42.270
I thought I was done for,

06:43.870 --> 06:45.110
but he appeared.

06:47.290 --> 06:48.880
I've practiced martial arts
since I was young.

06:48.880 --> 06:49.870
I started practicing with a sword

06:49.870 --> 06:51.130
as soon as I could walk.

06:51.950 --> 06:52.830
Yet he killed those men

06:52.830 --> 06:54.830
in a single move—men I couldn't beat

06:54.830 --> 06:56.360
even with everything I had.

06:57.240 --> 06:58.600
I didn't even see

06:58.600 --> 06:59.510
how he did it.

07:00.630 --> 07:02.270
From that moment on, I knew

07:02.900 --> 07:04.220
he was no mortal.

07:10.390 --> 07:11.720
And then what happened?

07:12.810 --> 07:13.610
Then...

07:15.390 --> 07:16.440
he left.

07:17.680 --> 07:18.950
And never came back.

07:20.720 --> 07:22.040
Those masked men died.

07:23.070 --> 07:23.950
But I knew

07:24.630 --> 07:26.230
my enemy was still out there—

07:27.310 --> 07:28.950
the county magistrate.

07:30.430 --> 07:31.890
He had embezzled tax money

07:32.040 --> 07:33.970
and couldn't cover the shortfall,

07:34.430 --> 07:37.159
so he turned to plundering
the common people's wealth.

07:37.159 --> 07:39.690
He had his men
disguise themselves as bandits

07:40.040 --> 07:42.440
and rob people of
their money and property.

07:51.270 --> 07:52.270
After that night,

07:54.390 --> 07:56.040
all that remained of my household

07:56.040 --> 07:57.750
was me, a young attendant,

07:59.070 --> 08:00.190
and a stable hand.

08:03.190 --> 08:05.870
They're the attendant and the cook now.

08:07.070 --> 08:09.530
Fearing our enemy
would come after us again,

08:09.600 --> 08:10.830
we left.

08:11.800 --> 08:12.510
Then,

08:13.800 --> 08:14.560
we found

08:14.560 --> 08:15.560
a secluded valley

08:16.160 --> 08:18.360
and devoted ourselves to martial arts.

08:18.750 --> 08:19.560
We trained

08:21.830 --> 08:22.950
for five years.

08:25.360 --> 08:26.360
Five years later,

08:27.000 --> 08:29.260
we came back after mastering the skills.

08:29.630 --> 08:32.159
We tracked down our enemy
and had our revenge.

08:32.390 --> 08:33.990
After that, we left for good.

08:41.000 --> 08:42.000
Then you came here

08:42.360 --> 08:44.020
and opened the Safe Haven Inn?

08:46.040 --> 08:48.930
[Safe Haven Inn:
Your Safety is Guaranteed.

08:52.390 --> 08:53.920
Got to make a living, right?

08:56.000 --> 08:57.200
Actually,

08:58.270 --> 09:00.130
I never thought I'd see him again.

09:01.670 --> 09:02.440
I know

09:03.240 --> 09:04.550
he's no ordinary man.

09:06.870 --> 09:09.120
He might be a cultivator,

09:10.200 --> 09:12.960
or perhaps an immortal of the Youhu Clan.

09:14.030 --> 09:15.120
Or maybe...

09:20.120 --> 09:21.650
It doesn't matter anymore.

09:24.600 --> 09:26.660
I know we belong to different worlds.

09:27.150 --> 09:29.030
We were never meant to be.

09:35.870 --> 09:37.470
The girl upstairs in the room

09:38.480 --> 09:40.140
is the one he loves, isn't she?

09:42.440 --> 09:43.770
What makes you say that?

09:45.790 --> 09:47.670
When he carried her in just now,

09:48.150 --> 09:49.440
he looked so tense.

09:50.270 --> 09:51.270
In his eyes,

09:52.320 --> 09:53.520
there was tenderness

09:53.670 --> 09:54.750
and heartache.

09:57.360 --> 09:58.600
We were acquainted.

09:59.750 --> 10:01.670
Everyone at the escort agency was

10:01.790 --> 10:03.520
quite kind to him as a neighbor.

10:04.000 --> 10:06.440
But even when my whole family
was slaughtered,

10:06.440 --> 10:08.240
I never saw that look in his eyes.

10:11.320 --> 10:12.000
Perhaps.

10:13.320 --> 10:14.780
He probably does like her.

10:22.440 --> 10:23.320
It's a pity

10:24.750 --> 10:26.350
they're also not meant to be.

11:15.320 --> 11:16.050
She's drunk.

11:17.150 --> 11:18.340
She wanted to drink it herself.

11:18.340 --> 11:19.400
I didn't force her.

11:23.960 --> 11:25.320
She didn't even drink that much.

11:25.320 --> 11:27.050
Who knew she'd end up like this?

11:27.150 --> 11:28.750
The attendant's gone to
make her some hangover soup.

11:28.750 --> 11:29.910
Once we get it into her,

11:29.910 --> 11:30.970
she should wake up.

11:33.790 --> 11:35.250
But it's understandable.

11:35.270 --> 11:38.030
Years of buried heartbreak
crashing down all at once—

11:38.030 --> 11:39.240
that's no joke.

11:40.600 --> 11:41.360
Did you know

11:42.200 --> 11:44.080
she hasn't married all these years

11:44.080 --> 11:46.480
because she still
carries you in her heart?

11:48.840 --> 11:49.500
Look at you.

11:50.000 --> 11:51.930
See how much damage you've caused.

11:53.080 --> 11:53.680
Oh, right,

11:54.720 --> 11:55.870
how is Xin upstairs?

11:57.240 --> 11:58.720
I've already fed her the blood.

11:58.720 --> 11:59.850
She'll be fine soon.

12:03.200 --> 12:03.960
Your blood

12:04.440 --> 12:06.170
is a divine remedy for healing.

12:06.550 --> 12:08.080
But have you thought about this?

12:08.080 --> 12:09.240
What are you going to do

12:09.240 --> 12:10.240
when she wakes up?

12:12.080 --> 12:14.150
She thought you were dead

12:14.480 --> 12:15.960
and risked her life to save you.

12:15.960 --> 12:17.670
Now here you are, perfectly fine.

12:17.670 --> 12:18.630
Even a fool

12:18.750 --> 12:20.350
would know something's off.

12:20.440 --> 12:21.300
Not to mention,

12:21.550 --> 12:23.270
she saw your face last night.

12:27.000 --> 12:28.530
Why don't you just run away?

12:29.960 --> 12:30.630
Run away?

12:32.790 --> 12:33.360
Yes!

12:34.000 --> 12:34.720
Run.

12:36.000 --> 12:37.410
Clean and simple.

12:37.790 --> 12:39.390
No one will ever find you.

12:41.440 --> 12:42.030
Please, enjoy, sirs.

12:42.030 --> 12:43.360
-I'll take her back first.
-You ungrateful thing...

12:43.360 --> 12:44.200
Okay, okay.

12:44.480 --> 12:46.720
You heartless wretch...

12:50.720 --> 12:53.240
They say a good drink
can wash away all sorrow.

12:53.240 --> 12:54.170
It works for her.

12:55.320 --> 12:56.780
And it'll work for you too.

13:20.790 --> 13:21.910
His Majesty has decreed

13:21.910 --> 13:23.750
Liang Wenjing, Minister of
the Court of Judicial Review,

13:23.750 --> 13:24.840
has abused his power for personal gain

13:24.840 --> 13:26.200
and framed loyal officials.

13:26.200 --> 13:28.360
The Liang family is hereby sentenced to
confiscation of property and clan extermination.

13:28.360 --> 13:30.510
His eldest son, Liang Quan,
and second son, Liang Zhong,

13:30.510 --> 13:31.910
have both been captured
and put in the imperial prison.

13:31.910 --> 13:33.240
Anyone who dares obstruct

13:33.240 --> 13:35.170
will be punished as an accomplice!

13:36.270 --> 13:36.730
My Lord,

13:36.750 --> 13:37.770
we wouldn't dare! We wouldn't dare!

13:37.770 --> 13:38.200
Search!

13:38.200 --> 13:39.130
Please spare us!

13:49.940 --> 13:52.920
[Foot of Tianyin Mountain]

14:13.960 --> 14:15.160
Your face is injured.

14:15.510 --> 14:16.710
Bandage it with that.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.860
Something happened outside?

14:48.910 --> 14:50.840
Likely to do with the Liang household.

14:50.840 --> 14:52.370
It has nothing to do with us.

14:54.920 --> 14:56.050
How are you feeling?

14:56.270 --> 14:57.530
Do you still feel weak?

14:57.960 --> 14:59.670
His palm strike was very powerful.

14:59.670 --> 15:01.130
My Qihai has been damaged.

15:01.390 --> 15:03.850
I'm afraid it will take some time
to recover.

15:04.120 --> 15:04.780
Senior Jin,

15:05.310 --> 15:06.030
could you please fetch me

15:06.030 --> 15:07.360
another Yangyuan Pill?

15:28.960 --> 15:31.270
That master's techniques
were extraordinary

15:31.270 --> 15:31.960
and didn't look like

15:31.960 --> 15:33.960
any of the Twelve Immortal Sects' arts.

15:33.960 --> 15:36.000
Senior Jin, you've traveled
the martial world—

15:36.000 --> 15:37.720
have you ever heard of him?

15:40.200 --> 15:41.800
All things come full circle.

15:41.910 --> 15:43.240
However the road winds,

15:43.870 --> 15:45.330
we are bound to meet again.

15:50.320 --> 15:51.120
What's wrong?

15:52.440 --> 15:53.970
It's the court's soldiers.

15:54.060 --> 15:54.960
Who knows

15:55.150 --> 15:57.150
what has come over Emperor Zong Din?

15:57.440 --> 15:58.150
He suddenly wants to reverse the verdict

15:58.150 --> 15:59.840
against that female cultivator's husband.

15:59.840 --> 16:01.790
The entire Liang household
has been arrested,

16:01.790 --> 16:03.480
sentenced to extermination,
and had all their property confiscated.

16:03.480 --> 16:04.680
Reverse the verdict?

16:06.270 --> 16:06.840
Yes.

16:07.960 --> 16:09.840
They've also sent people to find us,

16:09.840 --> 16:10.840
claiming that the female cultivator

16:10.840 --> 16:11.770
was sent by them.

16:12.270 --> 16:13.480
Killing those four officials

16:13.480 --> 16:14.790
was also the Emperor's order.

16:14.790 --> 16:15.270
They say it doesn't count as

16:15.270 --> 16:17.200
the immortal sects
interfering in mortal affairs.

16:17.200 --> 16:19.860
and that we needn't
concern ourselves further.

16:19.960 --> 16:20.600
That day, it was they

16:20.600 --> 16:21.930
who begged for our help.

16:22.000 --> 16:23.860
Now they come up with this excuse.

16:24.140 --> 16:24.840
We're left in a position

16:24.840 --> 16:26.970
where neither side is pleased with us.

16:28.840 --> 16:29.900
Someone is coming.

16:33.200 --> 16:34.400
Senior Bai is coming.

16:41.630 --> 16:42.320
Senior Bai.

16:43.200 --> 16:44.260
Please forgive me.

16:44.330 --> 16:46.730
[Bai Zongying, Tianyuan Sect]

16:44.630 --> 16:45.440
I'm late.

17:11.829 --> 17:12.640
You're awake.

17:15.750 --> 17:16.510
You should've called for someone

17:16.510 --> 17:17.640
if you wanted water.

17:18.349 --> 17:20.240
How are you feeling now?

17:20.349 --> 17:21.109
Are you hungry?

17:21.109 --> 17:22.910
Would you like something to eat?

17:55.030 --> 17:56.290
You don't need my help?

17:57.160 --> 17:57.920
You two, talk it out calmly.

17:57.920 --> 17:59.120
I'll be right here...

18:09.070 --> 18:09.640
Xin.

18:09.750 --> 18:10.750
Weren't you dead?

18:11.110 --> 18:12.510
Apparently not dead enough.

18:12.510 --> 18:13.970
Then let me finish the job!

18:22.830 --> 18:23.720
Calm down!

18:25.000 --> 18:26.400
Either you kill me today,

18:26.590 --> 18:27.590
or I kill you!

18:27.750 --> 18:29.070
This was all my fault.

18:29.440 --> 18:30.920
Punish me however you like.

18:30.920 --> 18:32.270
But let me explain first.

18:32.270 --> 18:33.790
Explain it in hell!

18:37.920 --> 18:39.510
That girl has just recovered
from her injuries.

18:39.510 --> 18:40.160
Go to hell!

18:40.440 --> 18:42.300
Aren't you going to do something?

18:42.680 --> 18:44.410
Even if I wanted to, I couldn't.

18:47.200 --> 18:49.400
What kind of grudge is this, seriously?

18:52.110 --> 18:53.790
Let them solve it themselves.

19:08.750 --> 19:09.880
Still want to fight?

19:10.350 --> 19:10.960
Fine.

19:12.030 --> 19:13.110
Since I can't move,

19:13.400 --> 19:15.260
I'll listen to your explanation.

19:15.830 --> 19:17.090
The day I was executed—

19:17.350 --> 19:19.210
death by 1,000 cuts—I didn't die.

19:19.270 --> 19:21.240
That's not where you should start, is it,

19:21.240 --> 19:21.880
Mr. Lu?

19:22.830 --> 19:23.690
In the capital,

19:24.110 --> 19:26.110
the one who saved me secretly
time and again

19:26.110 --> 19:26.840
was also you.

19:27.550 --> 19:29.110
Since you have such abilities,

19:29.110 --> 19:31.350
why did you allow yourself
to be imprisoned?

19:31.350 --> 19:33.440
Why did you submit to arrest
without a fight

19:33.440 --> 19:35.170
and suffer death by 1,000 cuts?

19:36.200 --> 19:36.830
I...

19:37.440 --> 19:38.370
have my reasons.

19:38.750 --> 19:39.680
"Reasons"?

19:42.160 --> 19:42.720
Fine.

19:43.350 --> 19:44.550
Then answer me this—

19:46.200 --> 19:48.200
you knew full well you wouldn't die,

19:48.880 --> 19:50.310
so why did you marry me?

19:51.240 --> 19:52.760
Why did you say those things to me—

19:52.760 --> 19:54.560
to make me believe you would die,

19:55.200 --> 19:57.060
to leave me carrying that burden,

19:57.440 --> 19:58.920
to fill me with resentment on your behalf,

19:58.920 --> 20:00.480
and even drive me to seek revenge for you?

20:00.480 --> 20:02.160
I didn't expect that you'd go that far.

20:02.160 --> 20:03.720
"Didn't expect?"

20:05.480 --> 20:07.480
You possess extraordinary skills,

20:07.880 --> 20:09.480
yet you allowed others to frame

20:09.480 --> 20:10.340
and punish you,

20:10.510 --> 20:12.350
subjected yourself to a cruel punishment,

20:12.350 --> 20:14.280
and made onlookers pity your fate!

20:14.750 --> 20:16.210
You knew you wouldn't die,

20:16.510 --> 20:18.240
yet you still chose to marry me—

20:18.520 --> 20:19.830
and asked me to burn incense

20:19.830 --> 20:21.550
and make offerings for you
after your death.

20:21.550 --> 20:23.480
What exactly were you trying to do?

20:23.740 --> 20:25.070
Were you toying with me?

20:27.960 --> 20:29.290
You said you'd explain,

20:29.830 --> 20:31.110
so explain it to me.

20:32.110 --> 20:33.400
I really want to know:

20:33.590 --> 20:34.830
when I risked my life—

20:35.550 --> 20:36.750
using my meager magic

20:37.000 --> 20:38.260
to seek justice for you

20:38.400 --> 20:39.590
and avenge you—

20:40.510 --> 20:42.240
what were you really thinking?

20:43.110 --> 20:44.570
Did you find it laughable?

20:44.750 --> 20:46.810
Or did you think I was a complete fool?

20:46.920 --> 20:47.780
I was grateful.

20:49.030 --> 20:49.790
Xin,

20:50.590 --> 20:52.050
I'm truly grateful to you.

20:52.970 --> 20:54.280
But I do have reasons

20:54.310 --> 20:55.510
I cannot tell anyone.

20:56.030 --> 20:57.830
They concern my life and safety.

20:58.270 --> 20:59.530
But please believe me,

21:00.030 --> 21:02.290
I never had any intention of harming you.

21:19.400 --> 21:20.800
Get some good rest first.

21:21.510 --> 21:23.710
If that resentment still hasn't faded,

21:24.350 --> 21:25.750
come find me in the lobby.

22:51.270 --> 22:53.310
Do not fight with anyone
for the next few days.

22:53.310 --> 22:54.000
Rest,

22:54.590 --> 22:55.640
and you will recover.

22:55.640 --> 22:56.900
Thank you, Senior Bai.

22:57.170 --> 22:58.200
I thought the Tianyuan Sect

22:58.200 --> 23:00.530
wasn't planning to send anyone this time.

23:01.350 --> 23:01.920
All the major immortal sects

23:01.920 --> 23:03.270
received letters from the court.

23:03.270 --> 23:05.070
Why wouldn't our Tianyuan Sect come?

23:05.070 --> 23:05.720
It's just that I

23:05.720 --> 23:07.240
was delayed by some matters,

23:07.240 --> 23:08.240
so I arrived late.

23:08.270 --> 23:09.800
If you had arrived earlier,

23:10.160 --> 23:11.760
we definitely could've detained
that female cultivator,

23:11.760 --> 23:12.550
and we wouldn't have

23:12.550 --> 23:14.280
ended up looking so miserable.

23:19.920 --> 23:21.240
With the cultivation levels
of everyone present,

23:21.240 --> 23:21.920
how could you fail to even detain

23:21.920 --> 23:24.070
a female cultivator
in the Qi Refining Stage?

23:24.070 --> 23:24.790
And earlier, the court

23:24.790 --> 23:25.510
urgently

23:25.510 --> 23:26.510
summoned us here,

23:26.610 --> 23:27.680
yet now they claim
that the female cultivator

23:27.680 --> 23:28.810
is their operative.

23:30.170 --> 23:31.570
What exactly is going on?

23:34.400 --> 23:36.330
That's the full account of events.

23:38.550 --> 23:39.350
You're saying

23:40.480 --> 23:42.350
the magical artifact she used
is similar to mine?

23:42.350 --> 23:42.830
Yes.

23:43.510 --> 23:45.540
She usually uses a crescent-shaped blade.

23:45.540 --> 23:46.880
When controlled by spiritual energy,

23:46.880 --> 23:47.640
it transforms into

23:47.640 --> 23:49.070
something like concentrated moonlight—

23:49.070 --> 23:50.330
exceptionally sharp.

23:50.550 --> 23:51.160
The first time

23:51.160 --> 23:52.160
we faced her,

23:52.350 --> 23:53.830
her artifact emitted
only one arc of light.

23:53.830 --> 23:55.110
The second time,

23:56.310 --> 23:57.240
there were two.

23:57.960 --> 23:59.550
That means her cultivation has advanced.

23:59.550 --> 24:01.310
She's broken through from
the Qi Refining Stage

24:01.310 --> 24:02.680
to the Foundation Establishment Stage.

24:02.680 --> 24:05.080
Mr. Bai, do you know
the female cultivator?

24:05.150 --> 24:06.400
I can't say for certain.

24:06.400 --> 24:08.070
Whether you're certain or not
hardly matters now.

24:08.070 --> 24:09.960
The court has ordered us to stand down.

24:09.960 --> 24:11.560
I'm heading back to the sect.

24:12.350 --> 24:13.830
The Immortality Pill is about to
be completed.

24:13.830 --> 24:16.160
Is your sect not going to
attend the event?

24:16.400 --> 24:18.060
The elders of our sect will go.

24:18.550 --> 24:20.280
Why am I even bothering to join?

24:20.880 --> 24:21.740
What about you?

24:21.750 --> 24:23.510
I still have some personal matters
to attend to.

24:23.510 --> 24:25.040
I'll head there afterward.

24:25.440 --> 24:27.060
Our sect will not be involved
in the event,

24:27.060 --> 24:28.520
so I won't be going either.

24:28.920 --> 24:29.520
All right.

24:31.240 --> 24:32.640
I'll take my leave first.

24:32.800 --> 24:33.300
The court

24:33.300 --> 24:34.920
summoned us here to address this matter.

24:34.920 --> 24:36.160
Since they've chosen not to pursue it,

24:36.160 --> 24:38.270
there's no reason for us to keep pressing.

24:38.270 --> 24:40.790
As for that female cultivator,
she's nothing to fear.

24:40.790 --> 24:41.790
But the male cultivator by her side

24:41.790 --> 24:43.440
has unfathomable cultivation.

24:43.440 --> 24:44.640
Provoking him rashly

24:45.110 --> 24:46.310
might bring trouble.

24:49.550 --> 24:50.150
Farewell.

24:50.880 --> 24:51.810
I'll see you out.

24:56.160 --> 24:58.020
You're heading back to your sect?

24:58.640 --> 24:59.300
Where else?

24:59.750 --> 25:01.210
We messed this up so badly,

25:01.440 --> 25:03.110
and we don't even know their names.

25:03.110 --> 25:05.110
We're just going to leave it at that?

25:06.070 --> 25:07.000
What do you want?

25:08.240 --> 25:10.700
Naturally, we can't simply
leave it at that.

25:11.790 --> 25:12.590
Senior Bai,

25:13.240 --> 25:14.310
that night, I saw

25:14.650 --> 25:15.310
Junior Jiang wound

25:15.310 --> 25:17.110
that male cultivator with her sword,

25:17.110 --> 25:18.510
but in the blink of an eye,

25:18.590 --> 25:20.440
his wound healed completely.

25:21.070 --> 25:22.930
Don't you find that a bit strange?

25:24.960 --> 25:26.350
Healed in an instant?

25:26.590 --> 25:27.590
That's what I saw.

25:28.270 --> 25:29.440
But Junior Jiang's Chengying Sword

25:29.440 --> 25:30.700
is no ordinary weapon.

25:30.720 --> 25:32.030
Even a Nascent Soul cultivator

25:32.030 --> 25:32.960
couldn't heal immediately

25:32.960 --> 25:33.880
after being injured

25:33.880 --> 25:34.830
by it.

25:35.880 --> 25:37.140
What are you thinking?

25:37.270 --> 25:38.670
Maybe I'm just ignorant,

25:39.240 --> 25:41.240
but for a being
with such regenerative ability,

25:41.240 --> 25:43.240
I can only think of one possibility:

25:44.030 --> 25:44.720
a War Demon.

25:47.640 --> 25:48.640
A War Demon...

25:53.680 --> 25:54.940
Come on, have some tea.

26:11.590 --> 26:12.460
Xin,

26:13.240 --> 26:15.310
-actually, I…
-I've thought it through.

26:15.310 --> 26:16.230
It was my fault.

26:18.030 --> 26:19.830
When I joined the immortal sect,

26:20.200 --> 26:21.590
my master made me swear

26:22.550 --> 26:23.510
to never use magic

26:23.510 --> 26:25.310
to interfere in mortal affairs.

26:25.750 --> 26:26.680
I was too stupid.

26:27.270 --> 26:28.930
I could never make sense of it.

26:28.960 --> 26:30.160
I always thought that

26:30.680 --> 26:32.790
since I was fortunate enough
to learn the immortal magic,

26:32.790 --> 26:33.990
I should put it to use.

26:34.110 --> 26:35.840
Otherwise, it would be a waste.

26:36.480 --> 26:38.440
But there is too much injustice
in this world.

26:38.440 --> 26:40.370
The court can't reach everywhere.

26:40.590 --> 26:42.000
If I happen to encounter injustice

26:42.000 --> 26:43.440
and have the power to intervene,

26:43.440 --> 26:44.480
why shouldn't I?

26:45.790 --> 26:46.640
So...

26:48.640 --> 26:49.590
I made mistakes.

26:50.830 --> 26:52.160
Many times over.

26:57.310 --> 26:58.070
In the past,

26:58.640 --> 26:59.770
I refused to repent.

27:00.650 --> 27:01.960
I thought it was the rules
that were wrong—

27:01.960 --> 27:02.640
not me.

27:03.960 --> 27:04.790
But this time,

27:05.920 --> 27:07.380
I've finally understood.

27:08.110 --> 27:09.750
In this world, there are immortals

27:09.750 --> 27:10.750
and cultivators.

27:11.880 --> 27:12.830
There are also countless

27:12.830 --> 27:14.030
demons and monsters.

27:14.310 --> 27:15.330
People are hard to read,

27:15.330 --> 27:16.830
and life is unpredictable.

27:16.830 --> 27:18.890
Magic can easily disguise the truth—

27:19.400 --> 27:20.550
how can mortal eyes

27:21.480 --> 27:23.480
tell what is real from what is false?

27:24.160 --> 27:26.090
Act, and you risk making mistakes.

27:27.200 --> 27:28.930
Do nothing, and you cannot err.

27:29.640 --> 27:30.510
That's why my master

27:30.510 --> 27:32.310
told me to stay within my bounds.

27:34.920 --> 27:35.680
I didn't

27:36.070 --> 27:37.200
think that through.

27:37.720 --> 27:39.520
I didn't consider your feelings

27:39.680 --> 27:41.080
and ended up hurting you.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.030
We met by chance

27:44.920 --> 27:47.110
and should've just helped each other
and gone our separate ways.

27:47.110 --> 27:48.310
I overstepped

27:48.480 --> 27:49.880
and threw myself into it,

27:50.480 --> 27:52.140
stirring things up even more.

27:54.590 --> 27:55.310
Xin...

27:55.340 --> 27:56.070
I know

27:56.790 --> 27:58.050
you have your reasons.

27:58.960 --> 28:00.310
I'm the one who meddled.

28:01.030 --> 28:02.030
I broke the rules,

28:02.830 --> 28:04.230
so I should pay the price.

28:06.640 --> 28:07.770
Now I see it clearly.

28:09.550 --> 28:10.270
Lu Huai.

28:13.680 --> 28:15.340
I should just call you Lu Huai.

28:16.440 --> 28:18.570
Thank you for teaching me this lesson.

28:19.000 --> 28:20.330
I won't do it ever again.

28:21.720 --> 28:23.250
It will never happen again.

28:41.010 --> 28:45.840
♪ Spending a lifetime,
I ask myself what I first sought ♪

28:42.350 --> 28:43.160
Mr. Lu,

28:43.880 --> 28:44.830
from now on,

28:46.110 --> 28:47.200
we'll go our separate ways

28:47.030 --> 28:51.780
♪ What is it my heart truly desires? ♪

28:48.200 --> 28:50.600
and have nothing more to do
with each other.

28:52.290 --> 28:55.280
♪ Step by step up the immortal stairway ♪

28:55.690 --> 28:58.450
♪ Paved with countless lost souls ♪

28:58.730 --> 29:04.670
♪ Who would dare destroy the ladder
to immortality and end the path? ♪

29:05.010 --> 29:09.970
♪ The sun blazes over the earth ♪

29:11.000 --> 29:16.020
♪ Yet it cannot warm
every cold home below ♪

29:16.050 --> 29:19.650
♪ I've heard cries that rend the heavens ♪

29:19.800 --> 29:22.620
♪ I hear the shame of parting ♪

29:22.640 --> 29:25.200
♪ This immortal path admired by all ♪

29:25.230 --> 29:28.110
♪ Can exist, or not exist ♪

29:28.130 --> 29:30.790
♪ Once again I see
the world's cold indifference ♪

29:30.810 --> 29:34.060
♪ Bending what I've cherished
all my life ♪

29:33.400 --> 29:34.510
She's very sad.

29:34.550 --> 29:36.900
♪ I do not fear returning to dust ♪

29:35.590 --> 29:36.920
All color has drained from her.

29:36.920 --> 29:39.800
♪ I walk this path alone ♪

29:38.110 --> 29:38.880
What?

29:40.220 --> 29:43.000
♪ So that all may share in ♪

29:40.440 --> 29:41.640
I did the wrong thing.

29:43.030 --> 29:45.960
♪ The road to immortality ♪

29:43.270 --> 29:45.070
You're only realizing that now?

29:45.980 --> 29:52.640
♪ I fear not defying
immortal laws and sacred precepts ♪

29:46.000 --> 29:46.680
Go.

29:47.200 --> 29:47.750
Me?

29:48.720 --> 29:49.350
Go where?

29:49.750 --> 29:50.750
Use your magic

29:51.440 --> 29:53.370
to erase her memories of this time—

29:53.920 --> 29:55.270
make her forget me.

29:56.030 --> 29:57.200
Make it

29:58.070 --> 30:00.330
as though none of this had ever happened.

30:12.790 --> 30:13.680
I want that one.

30:20.510 --> 30:21.170
Attendant.

30:21.240 --> 30:22.900
I'd like to ask you something.

30:23.610 --> 30:24.400
Please go ahead, Miss.

30:24.400 --> 30:25.200
A few days ago,

30:25.400 --> 30:27.120
I heard a female cultivator had
entered the capital and killed people,

30:27.120 --> 30:28.380
causing a huge uproar.

30:28.550 --> 30:30.350
Do you know how it all turned out?

30:30.480 --> 30:31.240
That matter?

30:31.350 --> 30:32.640
That matter has already been resolved.

30:32.640 --> 30:33.510
His Majesty issued a decree

30:33.510 --> 30:34.640
stating
that the female cultivator's husband

30:34.640 --> 30:35.720
had been wrongfully convicted,

30:35.720 --> 30:36.590
so the case was dropped

30:36.590 --> 30:37.750
and was no longer being pursued.

30:37.750 --> 30:39.160
Several ministers involved

30:39.160 --> 30:40.560
were also investigated.

30:40.750 --> 30:42.110
Where is that female cultivator?

30:42.110 --> 30:43.640
That I don't know.

30:47.550 --> 30:48.480
Take care, Miss.

30:56.240 --> 30:57.100
Go find Senior.

31:36.620 --> 31:40.150
How did I break through to
the Foundation Establishment Stage?

31:51.070 --> 31:52.330
I should go to the back.

31:52.530 --> 31:53.850
The cook might need me.

31:53.880 --> 31:55.540
Stop right there. Don't move.

31:57.270 --> 31:58.030
Excuse me,

31:58.590 --> 31:59.720
where is this place?

32:08.790 --> 32:09.400
Enjoy.

32:12.350 --> 32:13.440
A few days ago,

32:13.550 --> 32:15.680
there was heavy rain in the mountains.

32:15.750 --> 32:17.000
When I was passing by,

32:17.400 --> 32:19.480
I found you unconscious in the rain,

32:19.720 --> 32:20.920
so I brought you back.

32:21.950 --> 32:22.950
You've been sick

32:23.270 --> 32:24.550
for more than 10 days,

32:25.000 --> 32:26.480
delirious with fever.

32:27.070 --> 32:28.270
It wasn't until today

32:28.270 --> 32:30.470
that you finally woke up clear-headed.

32:31.920 --> 32:34.400
Why would I have collapsed
in the mountains?

32:35.310 --> 32:37.680
I'm not so sure about that.

32:39.270 --> 32:41.830
Why don't you try to think back carefully?

32:48.750 --> 32:51.680
I remember I went down the mountain
for some business

32:51.810 --> 32:53.470
and visited my aunt on the way.

32:54.160 --> 32:55.490
But my aunt passed away.

32:56.200 --> 32:57.550
I arranged her funeral,

32:58.200 --> 32:59.400
left Wei County,

32:59.720 --> 33:01.000
and then continued my journey

33:01.000 --> 33:02.260
to handle my business.

33:02.590 --> 33:05.000
And then I passed through here.

33:05.750 --> 33:07.350
I was overwhelmed with grief

33:07.720 --> 33:08.980
and caught in the rain,

33:09.000 --> 33:10.400
so I fell ill?

33:11.550 --> 33:11.950
Right.

33:12.310 --> 33:13.270
That must be it.

33:13.750 --> 33:15.480
That's exactly what happened.

33:17.790 --> 33:18.790
That's not right.

33:18.920 --> 33:19.680
I was sick,

33:20.030 --> 33:22.160
but why did my cultivation level improve?

33:22.160 --> 33:23.880
I wouldn't know about that.

33:23.960 --> 33:25.660
The affairs of you cultivators

33:25.660 --> 33:26.790
are so mysterious.

33:27.030 --> 33:28.490
I can't make sense of them.

33:31.110 --> 33:32.440
Thank you for saving me.

33:32.960 --> 33:33.890
You're welcome.

33:33.920 --> 33:35.030
I'm glad you're alright.

33:35.030 --> 33:36.430
That's all that matters.

33:36.510 --> 33:39.040
Here, have some ginger
and brown sugar water.

33:47.920 --> 33:48.920
Come on, hurry up!

33:51.640 --> 33:52.880
Hurry up and load the goods!

33:52.880 --> 33:53.480
Sir,

33:53.880 --> 33:55.240
once this job is done,
you'll be rich, right?

33:55.240 --> 33:56.270
When you get back,
you'll finally be able to take a wife, eh?

33:56.270 --> 33:56.930
Sure thing.

33:56.960 --> 33:57.790
If you happen to know
any suitable young ladies,

33:57.790 --> 33:59.000
remember to introduce them to me.

33:59.000 --> 33:59.440
Okay.

33:59.790 --> 34:00.440
Father.

34:00.790 --> 34:01.830
My bamboo dragonfly...

34:01.830 --> 34:03.560
My bamboo dragonfly flew away.

34:04.160 --> 34:05.290
Hold on. I'll get it.

34:17.710 --> 34:18.760
Excuse me, please step aside.

34:18.760 --> 34:20.889
You're standing on something of mine.

34:24.360 --> 34:26.290
You need to go to the Central Plains

34:26.590 --> 34:27.440
to find a woman

34:28.280 --> 34:30.010
and pass along a message to her.

34:30.510 --> 34:31.440
Yes.

34:32.800 --> 34:33.989
The goods are all loaded.

34:33.989 --> 34:35.600
We can depart anytime.

34:35.630 --> 34:36.280
Okay.

34:38.360 --> 34:39.820
Who is our boss talking to?

34:40.030 --> 34:42.690
Judging by the clothes,
looks like a big client.

34:48.510 --> 34:48.920
Boss?

34:49.000 --> 34:49.429
Sir!

34:49.580 --> 34:50.150
Where are you going?

34:50.150 --> 34:50.920
What are you heading off to do?

34:50.920 --> 34:51.320
Boss!

34:57.070 --> 34:58.470
What are your plans next?

35:00.400 --> 35:02.530
The Immortality Pill is nearly ready.

35:03.070 --> 35:04.320
I came down the mountain this time

35:04.320 --> 35:05.880
to attend the Pill-Tasting Competition
at Chongling Valley,

35:05.880 --> 35:08.410
to request an Immortality Pill
for my master.

35:12.280 --> 35:13.880
It's probably for the best that she left.

35:13.880 --> 35:16.000
You two were never
on the same path anyway.

35:16.000 --> 35:16.920
What a pity, though.

35:16.920 --> 35:17.880
Such a good girl—

35:18.070 --> 35:20.930
it would've been nice,
even just to remain friends.

35:26.400 --> 35:27.000
By the way,

35:27.510 --> 35:28.930
news came from the capital.

35:28.930 --> 35:29.710
The little Emperor has ordered

35:29.710 --> 35:30.920
a thorough investigation into your case.

35:30.920 --> 35:32.360
Many of the officials involved

35:32.360 --> 35:33.920
have been dismissed and imprisoned.

35:33.920 --> 35:34.580
He also said

35:34.960 --> 35:37.400
Xin Mei was acting
under the court's orders,

35:37.400 --> 35:39.630
and the immortal sect
no longer needs to interfere.

35:39.630 --> 35:40.230
Looks like

35:41.000 --> 35:42.660
he's going to clear your name.

35:44.880 --> 35:45.410
Let's go.

35:48.920 --> 35:49.630
Wait for me.

36:07.320 --> 36:08.190
Officer,

36:08.670 --> 36:11.000
your sword is completely rusted through.

36:11.230 --> 36:12.830
It can't be sharpened at all.

36:12.960 --> 36:13.630
Nonsense!

36:14.150 --> 36:15.410
This is a divine sword!

36:15.550 --> 36:17.510
It came to me
through a rare stroke of fortune.

36:17.510 --> 36:19.190
This sword, drawing on
the spiritual energy of heaven and earth,

36:19.190 --> 36:20.760
can slay gods and demons,
feed on their blood,

36:20.760 --> 36:22.420
and split mountains and seas.

36:23.280 --> 36:24.710
It simply hasn't been used in a long time—

36:24.710 --> 36:26.070
it's been resting
and has gathered a bit of rust.

36:26.070 --> 36:27.590
How can it not be sharpened?

36:27.590 --> 36:28.110
Well...

36:28.190 --> 36:29.400
You see it yourself.

36:29.670 --> 36:31.760
I've been sharpening it for four hours,

36:31.760 --> 36:33.160
and it's still like this.

36:33.760 --> 36:34.280
That only means

36:34.280 --> 36:36.230
you haven't sharpened it long enough.

36:36.230 --> 36:36.760
Besides,

36:36.960 --> 36:38.630
you were the one who boasted

36:38.960 --> 36:39.670
that you could

36:39.670 --> 36:40.730
sharpen any blade.

36:41.880 --> 36:43.680
T-Then you'll have to pay extra.

36:50.710 --> 36:51.640
Unfortunately,

36:51.800 --> 36:52.880
those last two copper coins

36:52.880 --> 36:54.550
you just pocketed were my very last ones.

36:54.550 --> 36:55.070
You...

36:59.630 --> 37:01.510
You even dare to trick
a government official?

37:01.510 --> 37:02.320
At worst, you can

37:02.320 --> 37:03.250
throw me in jail.

37:03.710 --> 37:05.440
I only charged you two coppers.

37:05.710 --> 37:07.170
That's worth a day at most.

37:08.590 --> 37:09.280
You...

37:25.630 --> 37:26.690
Are you calling me?

37:27.230 --> 37:28.070
Who else?

37:30.520 --> 37:31.400
You see your savior standing right here

37:31.400 --> 37:32.800
and don't even say hello?

37:34.070 --> 37:35.270
Do we know each other?

37:36.150 --> 37:37.410
You really are something.

37:37.410 --> 37:38.400
If it weren't for me last time,

37:38.400 --> 37:40.000
would you even still be alive?

37:40.000 --> 37:40.760
Last time?

37:42.440 --> 37:43.360
I was the one

37:43.550 --> 37:44.880
who, with one strike...

37:45.070 --> 37:46.400
killed that centipede demon

37:46.400 --> 37:47.480
and saved your life.

37:47.480 --> 37:48.140
You forgot?

37:51.920 --> 37:53.320
What kind of look is that?

37:56.070 --> 37:56.800
Don't go!

38:02.230 --> 38:02.890
Pinwheels!

38:02.930 --> 38:04.510
Get your pinwheels!

38:14.320 --> 38:15.440
Wait for me!

38:15.960 --> 38:16.960
What are you doing?

38:16.960 --> 38:18.220
What's wrong with you?

38:25.110 --> 38:26.230
Don't drink the water.

38:26.230 --> 38:27.150
Don't drink the water.

38:27.150 --> 38:28.410
Don't drink the water.

38:28.440 --> 38:29.920
There's poison in the water.

38:29.920 --> 38:31.030
Don't drink the water.

38:31.030 --> 38:32.110
There's poison in the water.

38:32.110 --> 38:33.030
Don't drink the water!

38:33.030 --> 38:34.280
There's poison in the water.

38:34.280 --> 38:35.280
There's poison in the water!

38:35.280 --> 38:36.710
Don't... Don't drink the water!

38:36.710 --> 38:38.070
There's poison in the water!

38:38.070 --> 38:39.280
Why is this guy acting so weird?

38:39.280 --> 38:40.400
The water is poisoned?

38:40.400 --> 38:41.480
It can't really be poisoned, can it?

38:41.480 --> 38:42.840
We should stay away from people like him.

38:42.840 --> 38:43.710
Look, he fainted.
